WEBVTT

00:11.070 --> 00:13.430
[Tangjing]

00:15.110 --> 00:16.870
The New Policies of Empress Dowager Xiuli.

00:16.870 --> 00:18.120
From today on,

00:18.580 --> 00:20.260
Biantang abolishes slavery.

00:20.800 --> 00:22.930
The slave trade is hereby prohibited.

00:33.670 --> 00:34.600
Yuequn Academy

00:34.710 --> 00:37.710
is a martial arts academy for women
founded by Empress Dowager Xiuli.

00:37.710 --> 00:40.000
It aims to provide
freed female slaves with the chance

00:40.000 --> 00:42.460
to learn martial arts
and practical skills,

00:42.670 --> 00:44.920
so they may have a craft to rely on.

00:44.960 --> 00:46.420
Those who wish to learn martial arts,

00:46.420 --> 00:48.280
please line up
at the 1st registration point.

00:48.280 --> 00:50.750
Those who wish to learn music or tea arts,

00:50.750 --> 00:53.240
please register at the 2nd
and 3rd points respectively.

00:53.240 --> 00:54.970
Everyone is welcome to sign up.

00:57.200 --> 00:58.390
I'm so tempted.

01:01.560 --> 01:02.280
That's great.

01:02.280 --> 01:03.010
I'll sign up!

01:03.320 --> 01:04.760
I'll sign up too!

01:04.760 --> 01:05.820
Hurry, I'll go too!

01:06.120 --> 01:06.840
Count me in!

01:09.760 --> 01:12.430
These are all memorials opposing
the abolition of slavery.

01:12.430 --> 01:13.760
Several court princes

01:14.510 --> 01:16.000
and vassal princes from outside

01:16.000 --> 01:18.480
are submitting memorials
several times a day.

01:18.480 --> 01:21.680
They are this close
to coming to the palace to make a scene.

01:22.280 --> 01:23.010
Don't worry.

01:23.760 --> 01:25.680
With you and Song Cheng protecting me,

01:25.680 --> 01:26.810
they wouldn't dare.

01:26.840 --> 01:28.350
We've hurt their interests,

01:28.350 --> 01:30.400
so naturally they need a place
to vent their anger.

01:30.400 --> 01:32.560
Before, I only thought
Biantang was prosperous

01:32.560 --> 01:33.759
and its people lived in peace,

01:33.759 --> 01:35.310
making it different from Great Yong.

01:35.310 --> 01:38.240
I didn't expect
that this decree abolishing slavery

01:38.350 --> 01:40.610
would expose so many acts of oppression.

01:41.509 --> 01:42.200
Biantang

01:43.490 --> 01:45.490
is just like this dress I'm wearing.

01:45.789 --> 01:47.039
It looks exquisite,

01:47.590 --> 01:49.350
but every piece of silk and thread,

01:49.350 --> 01:50.680
every pattern and embroidery on it,

01:50.680 --> 01:51.920
was sewn by the female slaves

01:51.920 --> 01:53.229
in the weaving workshop.

01:53.229 --> 01:55.039
Look at the former Crown Prince's Mansion.

01:55.039 --> 01:56.400
It looked glamorous,

01:57.039 --> 01:59.310
but weren't all those maids and concubines

01:59.310 --> 02:00.310
just slaves carefully crafted

02:00.310 --> 02:01.950
by their masters?

02:02.510 --> 02:04.240
If their masters were unhappy,

02:04.310 --> 02:06.770
they would still be beaten,
killed, or sold.

03:27.120 --> 03:32.350
[REBIRTH]

03:32.860 --> 03:35.400
[Episode 24]

03:36.280 --> 03:37.000
Flowers!

03:38.190 --> 03:39.310
Buy a bouquet!

03:39.470 --> 03:40.030
Go away.

03:40.360 --> 03:41.280
Go sell them somewhere else.

03:41.280 --> 03:42.840
No one wants your flowers here.

03:42.840 --> 03:43.360
Wait.

03:43.360 --> 03:44.150
Flowers!

03:45.400 --> 03:46.840
Please, buy one.

03:47.030 --> 03:48.590
These flowers are beautiful.

03:48.590 --> 03:49.190
Miss,

03:49.400 --> 03:50.360
I want a bouquet.

03:52.120 --> 03:52.840
How much?

03:59.630 --> 04:00.280
Linlang?

04:00.840 --> 04:02.170
My skills are inferior.

04:02.200 --> 04:03.360
Just kill me.

04:03.750 --> 04:04.960
Who sent you?

04:05.140 --> 04:06.300
No one.

04:06.870 --> 04:08.310
I hate you so much

04:08.310 --> 04:09.120
and want to kill you.

04:09.120 --> 04:09.840
Why?

04:10.360 --> 04:11.560
You killed Zhan Ziyu,

04:11.910 --> 04:13.630
leaving my sisters and me nowhere to go.

04:13.630 --> 04:15.630
We've been orphans since childhood.

04:15.630 --> 04:16.800
If Zhan Ziyu hadn't bought us

04:16.800 --> 04:17.950
and placed us
in the Crown Prince's Mansion,

04:17.950 --> 04:19.750
we wouldn't have had a good life.

04:19.870 --> 04:22.140
Now we have nowhere to go.

04:22.630 --> 04:23.680
As we grow older,

04:23.730 --> 04:25.190
we will soon lose our youth

04:25.430 --> 04:27.890
and beauty,
and won't be able to marry again.

04:28.160 --> 04:29.800
This is all because of you!

04:35.360 --> 04:36.000
How was it?

04:36.000 --> 04:36.600
How was it?

04:36.600 --> 04:37.530
Did you succeed?

04:47.560 --> 04:48.490
I came here today

04:48.920 --> 04:49.860
not to kill,

04:50.159 --> 04:51.390
but to recruit workers.

04:51.390 --> 04:52.430
Recruit?

04:52.430 --> 04:53.430
What kind of work?

04:55.680 --> 04:58.070
We opened a Yuequn Academy in Tangjing.

04:58.390 --> 05:00.070
It aims to teach women martial arts,

05:00.070 --> 05:02.310
tea arts, and other livelihood skills.

05:02.800 --> 05:04.950
I know your abilities.

05:05.190 --> 05:06.270
If you're willing,

05:06.720 --> 05:09.160
you can be female teachers
at Yuequn Academy.

05:09.160 --> 05:11.490
From then on, even without relying on men,

05:11.600 --> 05:12.920
you can be self-reliant.

05:12.920 --> 05:14.360
Female teachers? My foot!

05:14.360 --> 05:14.950
Bah!

05:15.310 --> 05:17.840
You must be tricking us
into working for free.

05:18.270 --> 05:20.130
I'm not going to teach any skills.

05:20.360 --> 05:22.350
We've been slaves since childhood,

05:22.350 --> 05:26.230
learning only how to serve men
with our looks.

05:27.040 --> 05:28.040
What do you know?

05:28.200 --> 05:31.000
Only by relying on our looks
can we live a good life.

05:31.680 --> 05:34.430
You can rely on your youth and beauty now.

05:34.720 --> 05:36.190
But what about when you get old?

05:36.190 --> 05:38.190
How many years
can you keep living in luxury?

05:38.190 --> 05:39.460
That's why we need to find a rich husband

05:39.460 --> 05:41.310
as soon as possible
while we are still young.

05:41.310 --> 05:42.830
And it's best to have a child or two.

05:42.830 --> 05:43.510
This way,

05:44.310 --> 05:46.040
we'll have long-term support.

05:47.600 --> 05:48.510
She's right.

05:48.950 --> 05:50.159
Everyone has their own ambitions.

05:50.159 --> 05:52.120
We just want to marry rich men,

05:52.120 --> 05:53.920
even if it's just as concubines.

05:54.510 --> 05:55.720
You always claim

05:55.720 --> 05:57.070
that you respect what women want,

05:57.070 --> 05:58.800
so why not respect our wishes?

05:59.190 --> 06:01.120
Since I have ruined your lives,

06:01.310 --> 06:03.640
I will arrange suitable husbands for you.

06:05.800 --> 06:07.600
Here are the noblemen in Tangjing

06:07.600 --> 06:09.830
who are of marriageable age,

06:10.390 --> 06:12.160
in their prime, and seeking wives

06:12.160 --> 06:13.190
or concubines.

06:19.190 --> 06:21.070
I'm not asking for someone
incredibly handsome,

06:21.070 --> 06:23.190
but they shouldn't look so ugly.

06:23.430 --> 06:25.090
Are you fooling us on purpose?

06:25.310 --> 06:26.680
Are you fooling us?

06:26.830 --> 06:29.720
There are 930 noblemen in the capital.

06:30.500 --> 06:31.800
Excluding those with obvious disabilities,

06:31.800 --> 06:34.230
wife-beaters, alcoholics, and gamblers,

06:34.270 --> 06:36.220
the remaining are these 35 men.

06:36.480 --> 06:38.159
If any of them catches your eye,

06:38.159 --> 06:40.690
I will arrange a meeting for you
immediately.

06:41.159 --> 06:42.040
Actually,

06:42.240 --> 06:44.570
we don't necessarily have to get married.

06:45.310 --> 06:45.920
Right.

06:46.240 --> 06:47.000
Sisters,

06:47.570 --> 06:51.480
we women can only find a way out—

06:51.480 --> 06:52.880
By relying on ourselves!

06:54.480 --> 06:55.940
Are you really not going to

06:55.960 --> 06:57.620
take another look and choose?

06:59.310 --> 07:00.760
Thank you for your kindness, Your Majesty.

07:00.760 --> 07:03.650
We will go to Yuequn Academy tomorrow
to find a job.

07:03.820 --> 07:05.230
Sisters, let's go!

07:06.600 --> 07:07.240
Wait.

07:10.980 --> 07:13.580
This is the deed
to the restaurant Li Ce bought.

07:13.800 --> 07:15.750
He couldn't bear to see women suffer.

07:15.750 --> 07:18.190
If you can run this restaurant well,

07:18.630 --> 07:21.090
it would be considered
fulfilling his wish.

07:31.190 --> 07:31.950
It's mine!

07:34.590 --> 07:35.230
It's mine!

07:43.159 --> 07:44.870
Move! Hurry!

07:46.800 --> 07:47.530
Move faster!

07:47.830 --> 07:48.510
Stand up!

07:48.950 --> 07:49.750
Young Master,

07:49.840 --> 07:50.720
I've found out.

07:50.780 --> 07:53.070
They say too many people died
mining black gold.

07:53.070 --> 07:54.750
Now the civilians
inside and outside the city

07:54.750 --> 07:56.260
are all being captured as slaves.

07:56.260 --> 07:58.310
If a household fails to hand someone over,

07:58.310 --> 08:00.040
they will all be taken away directly.

08:00.040 --> 08:00.600
Stop!

08:12.060 --> 08:12.730
Hurry up.

08:20.950 --> 08:22.000
Queen of Lingyue?

08:23.250 --> 08:25.830
I heard you've made a great contribution
to His Majesty recently.

08:25.830 --> 08:28.100
Are you here to receive a reward today?

08:32.510 --> 08:33.970
I was being presumptuous.

08:34.240 --> 08:35.750
The black gold mine you are in charge of

08:35.750 --> 08:37.870
has always made His Majesty worry.

08:38.020 --> 08:40.570
I heard you haven't mined much gold,

08:40.590 --> 08:42.190
but a lot of people have died.

08:43.440 --> 08:45.300
Hurry up. His Majesty is waiting.

09:06.670 --> 09:07.600
Your Majesty.

09:08.030 --> 09:10.360
The mining of black gold
hasn't stopped day and night.

09:10.360 --> 09:12.240
I have drafted more laborers,

09:12.600 --> 09:14.120
but the weather in the mountains
is too cold,

09:14.120 --> 09:16.180
and many horses have frozen to death.

09:16.510 --> 09:18.480
That's why we haven't been able
to meet the schedule.

09:18.480 --> 09:20.320
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

09:20.320 --> 09:21.790
If there's not enough horses,

09:21.790 --> 09:23.550
why not use slaves?

09:24.050 --> 09:26.510
One horse can be exchanged for 15 slaves.

09:26.550 --> 09:29.080
The slaves in Ximeng will never die out.

09:30.960 --> 09:32.470
If you can't bear to do it,

09:32.750 --> 09:35.010
you can have your clansmen mine for them.

09:35.320 --> 09:37.080
If I remember correctly,

09:37.120 --> 09:39.320
when I conquered the Lingyue stronghold,

09:39.320 --> 09:42.960
there were thousands of people.

09:42.960 --> 09:43.760
Your Majesty!

09:43.870 --> 09:45.480
The people of the Lingyue Clan
are innocent!

09:45.480 --> 09:47.510
In the previous trip to Biantang,

09:47.630 --> 09:50.200
you lost my entire Ximeng delegation.

09:50.480 --> 09:51.750
You said you killed Zhuge Yue,

09:51.750 --> 09:53.680
but you didn't bring back his body.

09:53.870 --> 09:55.510
I let you make amends for your mistakes

09:55.510 --> 09:56.810
by mining black gold,

09:56.830 --> 09:58.670
but you kept missing the deadlines.

09:58.670 --> 09:59.840
In my opinion,

10:00.030 --> 10:02.000
you've long forgotten

10:02.840 --> 10:04.840
your King.

10:19.240 --> 10:21.540
[King of Lingyue]

11:19.630 --> 11:20.390
Don't rush.

11:20.960 --> 11:22.630
There are more here.

11:34.510 --> 11:36.020
The King of Lingyue betrayed his people.

11:36.020 --> 11:37.080
He deserves to die!

11:37.510 --> 11:39.840
Your Majesty, why don't you just kill him?

11:39.840 --> 11:42.200
Do you really want him to die?

11:42.290 --> 11:43.960
He betrayed his clan.

11:45.440 --> 11:46.750
He deserves it!

11:55.750 --> 11:57.200
The neighboring Xiyi Tribe

11:57.200 --> 11:58.630
has been occupied by King Ximeng.

11:58.630 --> 12:00.760
Chief Xiyi was hanged
for refusing to surrender,

12:00.760 --> 12:02.830
and the Xiyi people were wiped out.

12:08.390 --> 12:09.270
Stay here

12:09.670 --> 12:11.200
and wait for me to come back.

12:11.480 --> 12:12.610
Where are you going?

12:12.830 --> 12:14.510
I'm going to the tribes to the east
for help.

12:14.510 --> 12:15.770
Ximeng has taken Xiyi.

12:16.000 --> 12:17.270
We're next.

12:32.600 --> 12:33.930
We share life and death,

12:34.080 --> 12:36.340
and we live and die with the Lingyue Clan.

12:37.040 --> 12:37.760
Wait for me.

12:38.630 --> 12:40.790
I will bring reinforcements back
to save you

12:40.790 --> 12:42.320
and the whole Lingyue Clan.

12:45.960 --> 12:48.560
There is a waterway
30 miles east of Mount Wumu.

12:49.080 --> 12:50.240
When we used to hunt,

12:50.240 --> 12:51.640
we often passed by there.

12:52.030 --> 12:53.430
If you set off from there,

12:53.720 --> 12:55.430
a round trip will only take 3 days.

12:55.430 --> 12:56.510
On the morning of the 4th day,

12:56.510 --> 12:57.720
when the sun rises,

12:58.160 --> 13:00.490
I will wait for you
at the top of Mount Wumu.

13:04.840 --> 13:06.730
Here is a pair of green-eyed birds.

13:06.730 --> 13:07.730
One for each of us.

13:07.910 --> 13:09.390
I hope they can bless us

13:10.910 --> 13:12.570
to get through this hardship.

13:15.530 --> 13:16.860
I'll be waiting for you.

13:36.320 --> 13:37.150
On the 4th day,

13:38.240 --> 13:39.510
when the sun rises,

13:40.000 --> 13:41.460
I will definitely be back.

13:42.960 --> 13:43.600
Hurry up!

13:44.440 --> 13:45.000
Keep up!

13:45.000 --> 13:45.750
Be careful. Don't fall.

13:45.750 --> 13:46.870
Hurry! They're coming!

13:46.870 --> 13:47.790
Wait for me!

13:56.600 --> 13:57.660
Protect the Queen!

14:02.320 --> 14:02.910
Your Highness!

14:02.910 --> 14:04.240
Ximeng is bypassing our defense line

14:04.240 --> 14:05.510
and attacking from the back mountain.

14:05.510 --> 14:07.120
The stronghold!
We can't hold the stronghold!

14:07.120 --> 14:07.750
Why?

14:08.120 --> 14:09.650
How did they know that path?

14:13.720 --> 14:14.580
Your Highness.

14:14.600 --> 14:16.880
It's... It's His Majesty.

14:18.320 --> 14:20.030
His Majesty surrendered to King Ximeng.

14:20.030 --> 14:22.160
He told King Ximeng about our defense.

14:27.430 --> 14:29.240
What did you say? Who?

14:31.270 --> 14:32.080
Impossible!

14:33.880 --> 14:35.550
Impossible! Impossible!

14:37.320 --> 14:40.050
His Majesty
went to the east for reinforcements.

14:40.290 --> 14:41.560
It's only the 3rd day.

14:43.200 --> 14:45.460
He will definitely be back on the 4th day.

14:46.070 --> 14:47.200
This is impossible.

14:49.120 --> 14:50.200
Impossible!

15:01.750 --> 15:03.190
I know how cruel you are.

15:04.360 --> 15:06.360
You can do whatever you want with me.

15:07.170 --> 15:09.770
But I will never surrender to you.

15:10.170 --> 15:11.820
I heard long ago

15:11.840 --> 15:14.570
about the same-clan marriage system
in Lingyue.

15:14.870 --> 15:18.730
The Kings and Queens of Lingyue
are from the same clan and are married.

15:19.180 --> 15:21.140
They live together from childhood

15:22.080 --> 15:25.200
and rule the tribe together
after they grow up.

15:29.630 --> 15:30.910
But why do you look

15:30.910 --> 15:32.870
so much stupider than the King of Lingyue?

15:32.870 --> 15:33.870
He knows what

15:33.870 --> 15:35.480
is best for his people.

15:35.630 --> 15:37.320
He used the defense map to trade

15:37.320 --> 15:38.840
for a way out for his people.

15:38.840 --> 15:40.080
And by doing this,

15:42.150 --> 15:45.680
do you want to ruin
his painstaking efforts with your own hands?

15:47.130 --> 15:48.390
He made his own choice!

15:49.910 --> 15:51.200
I made mine!

15:55.320 --> 15:57.840
Good. You have backbone.

16:00.890 --> 16:01.840
No!

16:04.850 --> 16:06.210
Your Highness! Your Highness!

16:06.210 --> 16:08.640
Your Highness, please save my child!

16:08.780 --> 16:09.960
Please, Your Highness!

16:09.960 --> 16:12.650
Save the child, Your Highness!

16:12.680 --> 16:14.630
Your Highness, please save...

16:16.430 --> 16:17.620
Mother!

16:19.360 --> 16:21.080
Alright!

16:25.400 --> 16:27.280
I agreed!

16:29.550 --> 16:31.510
If you let them go,

16:33.760 --> 16:35.560
I am willing to surrender to you.

16:37.320 --> 16:39.360
Your voice is too soft.

16:39.510 --> 16:40.840
I can't hear you.

16:42.080 --> 16:42.790
Kneel!

16:42.960 --> 16:44.390
Louder!

16:49.910 --> 16:50.860
I promise you...

16:51.360 --> 16:53.480
that if you are willing to let them go,

16:54.360 --> 16:55.630
I will submit to you.

17:03.270 --> 17:04.440
If he dies,

17:04.750 --> 17:06.030
your people will think

17:06.030 --> 17:07.890
that it was you who betrayed them.

17:08.250 --> 17:09.940
And you will bear this crime

17:10.420 --> 17:12.460
and live in humiliation.

17:15.720 --> 17:18.160
My reputation
hasn't mattered for a long time.

17:18.160 --> 17:19.819
As long as they can stay alive.

17:21.109 --> 17:23.240
As long as it can appease your anger!

17:25.510 --> 17:27.109
Not necessarily.

17:29.790 --> 17:31.000
You promised me

17:33.110 --> 17:35.510
that you would keep
the Lingyue Clan alive.

17:35.960 --> 17:38.000
Whether your people can live

17:38.510 --> 17:39.970
and how long they can live,

17:40.510 --> 17:41.480
the key...

17:42.510 --> 17:43.790
lies in you.

17:44.790 --> 17:45.880
I know.

17:46.480 --> 17:48.960
Many people died mining the black gold.

17:49.310 --> 17:50.790
The people of Ximeng

17:50.790 --> 17:53.480
have begun to resent me.

17:53.480 --> 17:55.830
But as you know,
this is just the beginning.

17:55.830 --> 17:57.720
To continue mining the black gold,

17:57.720 --> 17:59.680
I need more slaves!

18:00.480 --> 18:01.000
No,

18:01.880 --> 18:03.470
citizens.

18:13.270 --> 18:14.470
For Ximeng

18:15.030 --> 18:16.380
and the black gold mine,

18:16.960 --> 18:18.480
I have to let you

18:18.960 --> 18:21.120
make some sacrifices.

18:46.240 --> 18:47.200
Zhuge Yue,

18:47.790 --> 18:48.750
I'm sorry.

18:49.640 --> 18:50.350
Zhuge Yue!

18:58.880 --> 18:59.590
Zhuge Yue,

18:59.830 --> 19:00.760
where did you go?

19:01.000 --> 19:01.750
Zhuge Yue!

19:02.830 --> 19:04.000
Zhuge Yue

19:04.270 --> 19:05.750
is dead.

19:12.550 --> 19:13.030
No!

19:13.640 --> 19:14.310
No!

19:14.310 --> 19:15.110
Zhuge Yue!

19:45.030 --> 19:46.880
If Xiao Ran is quiet,

19:47.400 --> 19:48.860
he must be up to something.

19:58.310 --> 19:59.270
5,

19:59.510 --> 20:00.270
15,

20:01.000 --> 20:01.550
22,

20:02.480 --> 20:03.080
23.

20:04.350 --> 20:05.510
It's been 23 days.

20:05.510 --> 20:06.830
Why is there still no news?

20:06.830 --> 20:08.830
Logically, a round trip from Biantang
to Ximeng by fast horse

20:08.830 --> 20:10.200
should only take
a little over half a month.

20:10.200 --> 20:11.860
If everything goes smoothly,

20:12.370 --> 20:13.630
he should have finished this trip

20:13.630 --> 20:16.030
and be sitting in front of me
a long time ago.

20:18.400 --> 20:20.460
No, there must have been an accident.

20:29.860 --> 20:31.660
You messed up my counting herbs!

20:31.830 --> 20:32.690
Counting what?

20:35.310 --> 20:37.350
How many days has it been
since you last killed a patient,

20:37.350 --> 20:38.830
or since you last developed

20:38.830 --> 20:40.000
a lethal poison?

20:42.440 --> 20:43.570
Such a medicine pot.

20:43.720 --> 20:44.400
Boring.

20:45.000 --> 20:45.680
Fang Miaomiao!

20:45.680 --> 20:46.440
What?

20:53.830 --> 20:54.640
I have a

20:55.720 --> 20:57.240
super big problem

20:57.510 --> 20:58.970
that I need your help with.

20:59.720 --> 21:00.750
Super big?

21:01.070 --> 21:03.130
What problem do you need my help with?

21:08.640 --> 21:10.720
If the turtle shell faces up, I'll tell.

21:10.720 --> 21:12.720
If it faces down, I won't.

21:21.350 --> 21:22.210
It says to tell.

21:23.350 --> 21:24.950
No, no. Best two out of three.

21:44.240 --> 21:45.830
What exactly do you want to say?

21:45.830 --> 21:46.690
I want to say...

21:47.400 --> 21:49.270
Zhuge Yue is dying.

21:49.880 --> 21:51.290
Zhuge Yue is dying?

21:55.550 --> 21:56.790
What did you say?

22:04.030 --> 22:06.660
[Tangjing]

22:07.200 --> 22:08.800
This is the military tally
of the Xiuli Army.

22:08.800 --> 22:10.610
The other half is with He Xiao.

22:14.510 --> 22:16.160
When the two halves are put together,

22:16.160 --> 22:18.360
you can mobilize the entire Xiuli Army.

22:18.610 --> 22:20.790
I will bear your instructions in mind,
Your Majesty.

22:20.790 --> 22:22.320
The Emperor is still young.

22:22.440 --> 22:24.000
Many important matters in the court

22:24.000 --> 22:26.030
will have to rely on you, Grand Secretary Liu
and General Sun.

22:26.030 --> 22:27.410
If there's an emergency,

22:27.410 --> 22:28.870
you can have Fang Miaomiao

22:28.880 --> 22:30.740
go to Ximeng and send me a message.

22:31.370 --> 22:33.930
-Yes, Your Majesty.
-Yes, Your Majesty.

22:34.510 --> 22:35.240
He Xiao.

22:35.720 --> 22:36.270
Yes.

22:36.830 --> 22:38.400
You and the Xiuli Army will stay here.

22:38.400 --> 22:39.200
From now on,

22:40.030 --> 22:42.030
Biantang is your home.

22:42.600 --> 22:44.990
And the Xiuli Army is Biantang's army.

22:46.970 --> 22:49.580
But if Grand Secretary Liu and General Sun

22:49.640 --> 22:50.770
become dictatorial

22:51.310 --> 22:53.880
and abuse their power,

22:54.830 --> 22:56.760
you must help me keep an eye on them.

22:56.920 --> 22:57.720
Your Majesty,

22:58.110 --> 23:00.310
you'd better say that behind our backs.

23:00.350 --> 23:02.510
Otherwise, we'll feel very awkward.

23:04.720 --> 23:05.400
From now on,

23:06.840 --> 23:08.370
I'll be counting on you two.

23:22.880 --> 23:24.110
Stone her! Beat her!

23:24.110 --> 23:24.830
Step back!

23:25.850 --> 23:27.750
It's all her fault! She spread rumors,

23:27.750 --> 23:29.090
forcing King Ximeng to mine gold

23:29.090 --> 23:30.360
and capture slaves everywhere.

23:30.360 --> 23:32.020
[Meng En, General of Ximeng]

23:30.450 --> 23:31.530
Damn witch!

23:31.590 --> 23:33.000
She offered schemes to King Ximeng,

23:33.000 --> 23:34.930
causing the deaths of countless people!

23:34.930 --> 23:35.790
Not only that!

23:35.790 --> 23:36.110
Step back!

23:36.110 --> 23:38.270
She even betrayed her own Lingyue Clan!

23:38.270 --> 23:39.750
She deserves this today!

23:39.750 --> 23:40.790
It's all because of you!

23:40.790 --> 23:41.750
Beat her to death! Witch!

23:41.750 --> 23:42.720
Beat this witch!

23:42.720 --> 23:44.110
Bad people get what they deserve!

23:44.110 --> 23:45.590
Karma! Karma!

23:46.310 --> 23:47.000
Witch!

23:47.470 --> 23:49.000
Witch! Beat her to death!

23:49.000 --> 23:50.000
Go to hell!

23:50.440 --> 23:51.590
Die, witch!

23:51.590 --> 23:52.650
Stone her to death!

23:53.440 --> 23:54.400
Witch! Witch!

23:54.400 --> 23:56.310
She deserves it! Beat her to death!

23:56.310 --> 23:57.590
You caused all this!

23:57.790 --> 23:58.480
Witch!

23:58.480 --> 23:59.510
Spreading rumors!

23:59.510 --> 24:00.310
Beat her to death!

24:00.310 --> 24:01.030
Get lost!

24:02.170 --> 24:03.170
Beat her to death!

24:03.310 --> 24:04.550
Damn witch!

24:04.880 --> 24:05.720
This witch!

24:05.720 --> 24:06.350
Witch!

24:06.350 --> 24:07.550
Beat her! Witch!

24:07.550 --> 24:08.400
Beat her to death!

24:08.400 --> 24:09.330
She deserves it!

24:10.070 --> 24:11.590
Witch! Serves you right!

24:11.750 --> 24:12.110
Witch!

24:12.110 --> 24:13.350
Heinous crimes!

24:13.590 --> 24:14.270
Witch!

24:14.270 --> 24:15.440
Die a horrible death!

24:15.440 --> 24:16.110
It's all karma!

24:16.110 --> 24:18.370
Get out of the way!
I'll beat you to death!

24:18.590 --> 24:19.160
Get lost!

24:19.200 --> 24:19.750
Get up!

24:21.070 --> 24:22.110
Serves you right!

24:25.640 --> 24:26.400
Murder!

24:38.590 --> 24:39.480
Murder!

24:40.000 --> 24:40.530
Let's go!

24:47.590 --> 24:49.120
Oh no! The prisoner is gone!

24:49.160 --> 24:50.470
She couldn't have gone far.

24:50.470 --> 24:51.140
After her!

24:51.170 --> 24:51.610
Yes!

24:51.960 --> 24:52.560
After her!

24:54.720 --> 24:55.250
Let's go!

24:55.790 --> 24:58.250
I didn't expect Wang Shi'er's trick
to work.

25:08.310 --> 25:09.510
I can't walk anymore.

25:09.590 --> 25:11.160
You go first. Don't worry about me.

25:11.160 --> 25:12.490
The horse is just ahead.

25:13.070 --> 25:13.720
Come on!

25:15.590 --> 25:16.120
Let's go!

25:23.270 --> 25:23.790
Hurry!

25:29.070 --> 25:30.200
Keep yourself safe.

25:31.110 --> 25:31.590
Hurry!

25:33.240 --> 25:33.920
She can't get far!

25:33.920 --> 25:35.180
-After her!
-Let's go!

25:46.350 --> 25:46.960
Stop!

26:20.880 --> 26:22.920
Whether your people can live

26:23.480 --> 26:24.940
and how long they can live,

26:25.510 --> 26:26.440
the key...

26:27.510 --> 26:28.510
lies in you.

26:28.530 --> 26:29.880
You witch!

26:29.880 --> 26:30.720
I'll kill you!

26:31.550 --> 26:32.310
Witch!

26:56.670 --> 26:57.640
This dagger...

26:58.610 --> 27:00.410
was for you to protect yourself.

27:00.760 --> 27:02.170
Who asked you to save me?

27:03.830 --> 27:05.030
You took me,

27:05.950 --> 27:08.950
and King Ximeng
will take his anger out on my clansmen.

27:09.040 --> 27:11.080
I can't let them suffer for me!

27:11.200 --> 27:13.000
Do you think you can protect them

27:13.590 --> 27:14.790
by dying?

27:15.090 --> 27:16.650
King Ximeng promised me

27:18.160 --> 27:21.270
that as long as I took the blame
for mining the gold

27:21.550 --> 27:23.240
and killing the slaves,

27:25.200 --> 27:27.000
he would spare the Lingyue Clan.

27:27.400 --> 27:29.240
When you agreed to surrender to him,

27:29.240 --> 27:30.240
he also promised

27:30.920 --> 27:32.380
to spare the Lingyue Clan.

27:32.790 --> 27:34.390
But what actually happened?

27:34.790 --> 27:36.440
I had no choice.

27:44.070 --> 27:46.400
You can only protect them
if you are alive.

27:48.200 --> 27:49.110
If you die,

27:49.590 --> 27:50.550
they will end up buried

27:50.550 --> 27:51.960
in the dark mines.

27:52.590 --> 27:54.520
I didn't come here just to save you.

27:54.550 --> 27:55.640
If you insist on dying,

27:55.640 --> 27:56.570
I can't stop you.

27:57.680 --> 27:58.830
Saving you today

28:00.030 --> 28:02.230
is repaying you for your past kindness.

28:02.510 --> 28:04.630
I will bring news of your death to Baze.

28:04.630 --> 28:05.260
Baze?

28:06.550 --> 28:07.680
Baze is still alive?

28:09.440 --> 28:11.030
He traveled thousands of miles

28:11.030 --> 28:12.690
to Tangjing to ask for my help.

28:15.270 --> 28:17.070
He should have recovered by now.

29:01.240 --> 29:02.790
Everyone thinks

29:03.400 --> 29:05.200
I betrayed the Lingyue Clan.

29:05.960 --> 29:08.000
Both the Lingyue Clan and King Ximeng

29:08.000 --> 29:09.350
want me dead.

29:10.480 --> 29:12.080
Great Yong and the Zhuge Clan

29:12.840 --> 29:14.240
also think I am a traitor.

29:15.320 --> 29:16.920
I will forever bear the shame

29:17.160 --> 29:18.820
of betraying Qingshan Manor.

29:24.310 --> 29:26.720
Actually, the one
who betrayed the Lingyue Clan

29:26.720 --> 29:27.880
was King of Lingyue.

29:28.310 --> 29:30.510
He secretly defected to King Ximeng,

29:31.200 --> 29:33.460
causing the Lingyue Clan to be defeated.

29:36.880 --> 29:38.920
We used to be deeply in love,

29:39.270 --> 29:41.680
but when he betrayed our clansmen...

29:49.000 --> 29:49.730
Zhuge Yue?

29:51.000 --> 29:51.680
Zhuge Yue?

29:52.130 --> 29:53.680
Is it the Blood on Snow acting up?

29:53.680 --> 29:54.350
Zhuge Yue?

29:54.960 --> 29:55.590
Zhuge Yue!

29:57.000 --> 29:57.550
Come.

29:58.020 --> 29:59.060
Let's get up first

29:59.200 --> 30:00.240
and get out of here now.

30:00.240 --> 30:00.920
Zhuge Yue!

30:01.750 --> 30:02.400
Zhuge Yue!

30:10.720 --> 30:11.400
Zhuge Yue!

30:41.600 --> 30:42.510
Get up!

30:48.510 --> 30:49.110
Zhuge Yue!

30:49.440 --> 30:49.840
Don't!

30:50.070 --> 30:50.640
Don't!

30:51.020 --> 30:51.960
Give it to me!

30:53.030 --> 30:53.750
Zhuge Yue,

30:54.480 --> 30:55.070
no.

31:01.000 --> 31:01.640
Zhuge Yue!

31:03.000 --> 31:03.920
Zhuge Yue!

31:04.440 --> 31:05.270
Zhuge Yue!

31:06.270 --> 31:08.430
This sword was for me to protect myself,

31:08.430 --> 31:09.950
not to hurt you!

31:10.350 --> 31:12.200
Give me some more time!

31:12.310 --> 31:14.310
I will find the antidote!

31:33.640 --> 31:34.230
Stop.

31:35.790 --> 31:36.310
Go.

31:37.330 --> 31:38.190
You, come here.

31:48.200 --> 31:49.330
What would you like?

31:49.570 --> 31:50.830
This one. And this one.

31:50.830 --> 31:51.440
Alright.

31:52.400 --> 31:53.120
Here you go.

32:47.140 --> 32:48.670
How did you find this place?

32:49.590 --> 32:50.830
You don't need to be nervous.

32:50.830 --> 32:51.830
I didn't bring anyone with me.

32:51.830 --> 32:54.290
Remember when we attacked
the Beiyu people?

32:54.960 --> 32:56.620
I was injured, and you saved me

32:57.000 --> 32:58.130
and brought me here.

32:58.790 --> 33:00.630
Although I was unconscious at the time,

33:00.630 --> 33:01.860
I vaguely remember some things.

33:01.860 --> 33:03.390
You're not here to catch me?

33:04.070 --> 33:05.070
You saved my life,

33:05.880 --> 33:07.410
so I am returning the favor.

33:07.830 --> 33:09.000
Go back with me now

33:09.270 --> 33:11.480
and hand the person in that room
over to King Ximeng.

33:11.480 --> 33:12.810
I will back you up and say

33:13.070 --> 33:14.960
that this was a trap you set

33:14.960 --> 33:16.160
to lure out Zhuge Yue.

33:16.270 --> 33:17.480
He saved my life too.

33:18.590 --> 33:19.590
I can't do this.

33:23.310 --> 33:24.670
What about your clansmen?

33:24.670 --> 33:26.170
For someone from Great Yong,

33:26.170 --> 33:29.030
are you going to sacrifice
the entire Lingyue Clan?

33:32.810 --> 33:34.610
Have you fallen in love with him?

33:35.800 --> 33:37.860
What nonsense are you talking about?

33:56.510 --> 33:58.040
The blood dove landed here.

33:58.830 --> 34:00.230
It should be in the woods.

34:17.469 --> 34:18.840
This is a Lingyue wood carving.

34:18.840 --> 34:19.840
It must be here.

34:39.469 --> 34:40.530
What are you doing?

34:40.670 --> 34:41.320
Stop it!

34:46.600 --> 34:48.929
If you keep fighting,
he will die for sure.

34:55.280 --> 34:57.480
She is performing bloodletting on him.

35:01.990 --> 35:02.880
Baze, let's go.

35:11.820 --> 35:12.820
How is he now?

35:37.630 --> 35:39.190
Thank you for your blood dove.

35:39.190 --> 35:40.520
We attacked you earlier

35:41.400 --> 35:43.130
because we misunderstood you.

35:51.400 --> 35:54.070
Although this courtyard
is in a wild forest,

35:54.760 --> 35:56.110
it is fully equipped.

35:57.030 --> 35:58.510
The hunting knives and bows in the room

35:58.510 --> 35:59.800
are also in pairs.

36:00.140 --> 36:01.100
I just saw

36:01.570 --> 36:04.360
the green-eyed birds
of the Lingyue Clan carved on them.

36:04.360 --> 36:06.230
This should be the place
where you and King of Lingyue

36:06.230 --> 36:07.690
used to rest when hunting.

36:08.670 --> 36:10.470
If you have time to notice these,

36:10.680 --> 36:12.960
you'd better figure out
how to save your man first.

36:12.960 --> 36:15.210
Is that wandering doctor actually capable?

36:15.210 --> 36:16.810
Can he really save Zhuge Yue?

36:17.710 --> 36:19.440
You should know better than I do

36:19.760 --> 36:22.290
that the poison of Blood on Snow
is incurable.

36:22.920 --> 36:23.590
Unless

36:24.360 --> 36:26.420
we get the antidote from King Ximeng.

36:27.150 --> 36:28.760
Then there's nothing we can do.

36:28.760 --> 36:30.760
There is a clearing behind this forest.

36:30.760 --> 36:31.920
If you don't mind,

36:32.060 --> 36:33.520
it can be his burial place.

36:34.290 --> 36:36.420
Don't you want to save King of Lingyue?

36:40.400 --> 36:41.110
I know that

36:41.960 --> 36:44.820
he's locked in the dungeon
of King Ximeng's Palace.

36:45.000 --> 36:45.860
I also know that

36:46.570 --> 36:48.680
he was also poisoned by the Blood on Snow.

36:48.680 --> 36:49.680
What do you want?

36:51.840 --> 36:54.510
I want to know King Ximeng's weakness.

36:56.550 --> 36:58.280
I'm sure you know how to help me.

37:00.690 --> 37:02.120
If you want to stay here,

37:02.810 --> 37:04.010
keep your mouth shut.

37:10.940 --> 37:12.650
If you interfere any further,

37:12.710 --> 37:13.960
I'll exchange your man's body

37:13.960 --> 37:15.820
for the antidote to Blood on Snow.

37:42.030 --> 37:43.090
Congratulations.

37:43.440 --> 37:45.630
You will become King Ximeng's women.

37:46.360 --> 37:47.340
Always and forever,

37:47.340 --> 37:47.860
I

37:48.030 --> 37:50.000
will stand by your side, Your Majesty.

37:50.000 --> 37:51.860
No one leaves here alive tonight!

37:52.010 --> 37:52.480
We are exposed!

37:52.480 --> 37:53.440
Don't run!

37:53.880 --> 37:55.590
Where is Chu Qiao?

37:56.030 --> 37:57.550
Zhuge Yue?

37:57.570 --> 37:58.340
All of this

37:58.590 --> 37:59.920
is over.
